        Developer Manual
        ================
        
        Note: You find a developer manual for raptus.article at 
        `raptus.article.core <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/raptus.article.core>`_.
        Please have look there if you need more information.
        
        raptus.article.default is a package, which provides a list of useful raptus.article
        features by default. So you just have to install this package with your buildout
        and the rest is provided by the package.
        
